TopicTitle: NO parts loading after update to patch 1.7.2

Articles.Content: Anyone have any idea whats going on? I have a modded install, that is unchanged from its well running state on 1.7.1, the update the 1.7.2 caused my game to only load the fuel ducts, and struts, NOTHING else loads. Worse yet, is that reverting back to version 1.7.1 leaves me with the same problem?

Sounds like something messed up in the update progress. Hard to say what's exactly going on without a log but going for a clean reinstall of KSP usually fixes such unusual issues. You can backup your mods and you should definitely backup your savegame though
Did a Clean install, game works as intended until I reapply my mods. Its clear something in my mods is messing with things. Is there a way for me to get a start up log and see where things go wrong?
